results.title: Live Laugh Love wreath sign
results.description: This Live Laugh Love sign is beautiful for your summer or spring wreath, It is sublimated and can be ordered in 3 sizes. These signs are very sturdy and on sublimated hard board or Mdf as some know it . They can be cleaned with alcohol or just a damp cloth. They are very versatile and will last for years. I recommend using glue on zip tie holders to hold them on the wreath these can be purchased at Amazon. They can be placed outside opn a covered porch as long as they are not rained on.  They come in 3 popular sizes but if you have a need for a different size message me I can make them to order. All sublimation signs are made of HDF :Also referred to as hardboard, a high density fiberboard (HDF) for flooring is a type of engineered wood product. It's made from wood fiber extracted from chips and pulped wood waste. HDF for flooring is similar but much harder and denser than particle board or medium density fiberboard (MDF) for flooring
